productText.text:
A fruity, delicious boost—80 mg. of caffeine from green tea and 1 combined serving of vegetables and fruit*


*8 FL. OZ. OF THIS JUICE PROVIDES 1 COMBINED SERVING OF VEGETABLES AND FRUIT ( ABOUT 2.5 OZ VEGETABLE JUICE AND 1.5 OZ FRUIT JUICE). 1 SERVING OF VEGETABLES OR FRUIT = 4 OZ (1/2 CUP).
DIETARY GUIDELINES RECOMMEND 2 1/2 CUPS OF A VARIETY OF VEGETABLES AND 2 CUPS OF FRUIT PER DAY FOR A 2000 CALORIES 
DIET.

productText.text: Every day, you set a new record for getting it all done. Refuel with a delicious boost: V8® +Energy Orange Pineapple.

productText.text: Every day, you set a new record for getting it all done. Refuel with V8® +Energy Orange Pineapple. Naturally powered by green tea and infused with sweet hints of citrus and tropical pineapple, V8 +Energy powers you up V8-style. It's rich in B vitamins, contains no added sugar, and provides a combined serving of vegetables and fruit in each can. The perfect go-to beverage for the perfect pick-me-up ... so you can be your best self all day long.

productText.text: Steady energy from green tea. That’s what V8 +Energy® is all about. The kind of energy that helps you get the most out of your day, provides a restorative boost, and helps you be present for the amazing life you’re creating. Not wired—but wakeful. Made with B vitamins and 80 mg. of caffeine from green tea, +Energy harnesses its great taste from a blend of vegetable and fruit juices. So take a moment to refuel. Whatever’s coming next, you’re ready.
